---
title: Which Profiler module should I open?
---
flowchart TB
  ROOT["Something is slow or wrong.<br/>Which module do I open?"]:::orbiter

  ROOT --> Q1{Frame rate below target?}
  Q1 -- "yes" --> CPU[CPU Usage module<br/>Hierarchy for averages · Timeline for spikes]:::planet

  ROOT --> Q2{CPU budget OK but GPU slow?}
  Q2 -- "yes" --> GPU[GPU Usage module<br/>+ Frame Debugger · check overdraw · confirm batching]:::planet

  ROOT --> Q3{Micro-stutters or GC spikes?}
  Q3 -- "yes" --> MEM[Memory module<br/>target 0 B GC alloc/frame · check Detailed sample]:::planet

  ROOT --> Q4{UI sluggish?}
  Q4 -- "yes" --> UI_M[UI module<br/>canvas rebuilds · batch breaks · TMP alloc]:::planet

  ROOT --> Q5{Physics overshoot or fighting custom integrator?}
  Q5 -- "yes" --> PHY[Physics 2D module<br/>should flatline · if not, a non-kinematic rigidbody sneaked in]:::planet

  ROOT --> Q6{Unknown hot method — no BeginSample yet?}
  Q6 -- "yes" --> DEEP[Deep Profile once<br/>find the hot method · wrap in BeginSample · shallow-profile forever after]:::neutral

